Interface FlipFitSlotDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlipFitSlotDAO
public interface FlipFitSlotDAOInterface
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for handling slot-related operations in FlipFit system. This interface defines methods for retrieving slots, adding slots, and fetching slots by specific criteria.
Author:
gamma-group
